  "original_title": "Navy commander meets Maldives delegation",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Navy commander meets Maldives delegation",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Defence Advisor designate at the High Commission of the Republic of Maldives in Colombo, Lieutenant Colonel Hassan Amir and the incumbent Maldivian Defence Advisor, Colonel Ismail Naseer called on Commander of the Navy, Vice Admiral Nishantha Ulugetenne at the Navy Headquarters on Friday (02nd September 2022).",
        "During this official interaction, Vice Admiral Nishantha Ulugetenne warmly welcomed Lieutenant Colonel Hassan Amir, the incoming Maldivian Defence Advisor and also expressed his gratitude and best wishes to Colonel Ismail Naseer, who is on the verge of his termination of duty in Sri Lanka.",
        "The cordial interaction drew to a close with an exchange of mementoes, signifying goodwill and cooperation.",
        "Suspect arrested after failed assassination attempt on Argentine vice president"
      ],
